Class LittlePrince

java.lang.Object
greenfoot.Actor
SuperSmoothMover
Being
Moving
LittlePrince
public class LittlePrince extends Moving
The LittlePrince class represents the character that walks around planets and jumps out of planets when all the baobab trees are destroyed. It extends the Moving class and has additional behavior related to health points, collision detection, and rotation.

Version:
v1.0
Author:
